title: Hotdoor CADtools v6.0 for Adobe Illustrator CS4
description:
Add-in for Adobe Illustrator (all CSx versions)

Vendor description:
Hot Door CADtools 6 introduces new precision drawing and measuring power for designers in a wide range of professions including graphic design, architecture, product design, sign design, and manufacturing. Developed and tested by design professionals, CADtools addresses industry needs with automatic linear, radial, angle, and Bezier curve dimensioning tools, numeric input for precision control, and easy-to use, integrated interface.
